items.title: Titan Q3 update: Consumer business grows 40% YoY; company adds 56 new stores
items.description: Titan Company's consumer businesses surged 40% year-on-year in Q3FY26, with international and domestic segments growing 79% and 38% respectively. The company expanded its retail network by 56 stores, reaching 3,433. Jewellery sales jumped 41% driven by price increases, while watches and eyecare also saw significant growth.
